2
00:00:23,590 --> 00:00:25,500
What is it?

3
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:28,910
What happened that you suddenly want to see me?

4
00:00:29,710 --> 00:00:32,540
You're the only one I can talk to.

5
00:00:35,090 --> 00:00:37,830
So, something did happen.

6
00:00:37,830 --> 00:00:40,650
Is he terminally ill or something?

7
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:43,980
He was lying when he said he was sick.

8
00:00:44,590 --> 00:00:46,980
Is he crazy?

9
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:49,390
Why would he tell such a lie?

10
00:00:49,390 --> 00:00:51,940
Seriously, what's wrong with him?

11
00:00:54,340 --> 00:00:56,750
I can see why you cut ties with him.

12
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:03,500
You get absorbed too easily.

13
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:08,410
How can you laugh?

14
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:15,410
You didn't laugh it off in front of him, did you?

15
00:01:17,530 --> 00:01:20,620
I wish I did.

16
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:23,210
This must be some kind of illness, too.

17
00:01:23,810 --> 00:01:27,080
Because we're friends, he jokes around,

18
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:29,500
treats me nicely,

19
00:01:30,270 --> 00:01:33,330
and he's by my side.

20
00:01:33,330 --> 00:01:38,140
But I get seriously angry and get hopes up. I feel stupid.

21
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:39,630
What?

22
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:46,020
When you suggested creating a webtoon, I should've said no, no matter what.

23
00:01:46,020 --> 00:01:48,470
I came out late at night.

24
00:01:48,470 --> 00:01:50,730
This is what you're telling me?

25
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:53,870
I've never said this to anyone.

26
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:57,290
But I keep doing it because you side with me.

27
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:04,230
Is there really an end?

28
00:02:05,550 --> 00:02:08,210
I don't know what's going on anymore.

29
00:02:09,950 --> 00:02:14,630
Were you cursed to be in unrequited love forever?

30
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:18,930
You want me to help you?

31
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:26,410
First of all...

32
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:50,700
What?

33
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,420
What's the deal?

34
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:55,140
It's nothing.

35
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:04,410
By chance, is that...

36
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,640
the Death Note?

37
00:03:10,260 --> 00:03:11,810
What are you saying?

38
00:03:11,810 --> 00:03:13,890
I write briefly whenever I'm taking a break.

39
00:03:13,890 --> 00:03:16,190
Don't write my name down.

40
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:22,360
Drink this.

41
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,170
I'm leaving.

42
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:27,400
Is this why you came?

43
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,240
Yes.

44
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:32,410
I'll be at the studio, and you'll stay here.

45
00:03:33,010 --> 00:03:35,150
We need to go to the same school.

46
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:43,750
