91
00:07:12,650 --> 00:07:13,970
Yes.

92
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:15,880
Of course...

93
00:07:17,450 --> 00:07:19,630
it's a happy ending.

94
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,580
Of course?

95
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:24,920
The unrequited love comes true?

96
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,240
