108
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:43,160
[What should I get Ba Woo for his birthday?]

109
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:46,180
[October 27 - Do Ba Woo's birthday]

110
00:08:55,490 --> 00:08:57,170
Ba Woo!

111
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:06,210
Doesn't running into each other often mean it's fate?

112
00:09:06,210 --> 00:09:10,060
- Isn't that too cheesy of a line?
- Yeah.

113
00:09:10,060 --> 00:09:11,650
Going to work?

114
00:09:13,210 --> 00:09:14,990
That's great.

115
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:17,790
Let me come with you.

116
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:20,420
I need an Americano.

117
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:34,270
Hello. Gosh!

118
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:35,790
- My gosh. My gosh.
- I hope so.

119
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:39,400
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

120
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,370
My gosh.

121
00:09:41,370 --> 00:09:42,520
Oh, no...

122
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,280
- Are you okay?
- I'm sorry.

123
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,550
Yes.

124
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:48,780
It's all dry. It's okay.

125
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:51,690
Look up a clothing store nearby.

126
00:09:51,690 --> 00:09:53,670
There's one five minutes away.

127
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:55,850
You're a good brother sometimes.

128
00:09:55,850 --> 00:09:58,140
What are you saying?

129
00:09:58,140 --> 00:09:59,950
See you later.

130
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:04,010
Seriously, you're troublesome.

131
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:09,770
- It's okay.
- I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

132
00:10:14,830 --> 00:10:16,600
What do I do?

133
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,620
You must've been shocked.

134
00:10:50,620 --> 00:10:52,970
But it could've been worse.

135
00:10:52,970 --> 00:10:55,700
Just think that.

136
00:10:55,700 --> 00:10:59,040
You've got to be kidding me.

137
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:05,820
- Are you crying?
- No, I'm not.

138
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:08,250
It's just embarrassing.

139
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:16,160
Why did I make a mistake in front of him?

140
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,910
In front of him?

141
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:31,640
By chance,

142
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:35,030
is your crush that person just now?

143
00:11:38,350 --> 00:11:43,580
Be positive and think you made an impression.

144
00:11:43,580 --> 00:11:45,850
How could I think that?

145
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:52,350
Do you have to worry about his sister, too?

146
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:55,810
Jung Ha Min is separate from his sister.

147
00:11:55,810 --> 00:11:57,750
You didn't spill coffee on him.

148
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:59,310
Think positively.

149
00:11:59,310 --> 00:12:00,550
Hold on.

150
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:05,260
I appreciate you comforting me, but I think you're mistaken.

151
00:12:06,060 --> 00:12:08,840
The person I like isn't Jung Ha Min.

152
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,910
It's that lady just now.

153
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:14,610
Start over.

154
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:17,450
Are you crazy?

155
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:20,290
You should've given her a complimentary drink.

156
00:12:20,290 --> 00:12:22,770
But you spilled coffee on her instead?

157
00:12:22,770 --> 00:12:28,820
Well, my hands were shaky because I was nervous.

158
00:12:32,580 --> 00:12:36,690
It's like I'm broken when I'm close to her.

159
00:12:36,690 --> 00:12:38,790
I say all sorts of random things

160
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:41,280
and I act strangely.

161
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:43,350
I just break.

162
00:12:43,350 --> 00:12:46,650
I really tried to do my best.

163
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:50,560
But the more I try,

164
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:53,530
something keeps going wrong.

165
00:12:53,530 --> 00:12:57,200
I'm totally screwed.

166
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:23,260
I did buy something.

167
00:13:23,260 --> 00:13:25,630
But would it make him feel uncomfortable?

168
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:32,540
Why is it so hard?

169
00:13:54,050 --> 00:13:55,670
What's with you?

170
00:14:11,430 --> 00:14:13,620
Let's talk for a moment.

171
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:36,430
What's your name?

172
00:14:37,230 --> 00:14:39,320
Ask Ba Woo.

173
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:41,430
Right.

174
00:14:41,430 --> 00:14:43,960
He won't answer your call, right?

175
00:14:46,850 --> 00:14:49,660
Did you know he named you "Stalker" on his phone?

176
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,450
If you like someone,

177
00:14:53,450 --> 00:14:56,760
