178
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:05,900
Does he find me annoying?

179
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:14,880
- You don't even know.
- Don't act like you know. I'll beat you up.

180
00:15:18,570 --> 00:15:23,690
Ba Woo and I've been friends since kindergarten.

181
00:15:23,690 --> 00:15:28,800
We've been friends all the way through college.

182
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:32,140
He never had a friend like me his whole life.

183
00:15:32,140 --> 00:15:34,210
And he never will.

184
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:42,880
You won't be friends in a few days, right?

185
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,540
What?

186
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,730
I told him to do that.

187
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:03,160
You stop bothering him.

188
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:35,110
<i>Why did you quit music?</i>

189
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:38,650
<i>Because it was unrequited love.</i>

190
00:16:42,770 --> 00:16:46,070
<i>He never had a friend like me his whole life.</i>

191
